Invocation Name: salary after college
des:
Do you want to know how college selection affects your likely salary after graduation?
Using Open Data from U.S. Department of Education, Alexa's Salary after College will tell you the top 5 colleges in each State ranked by median earnings of former students.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
